### Constructor Syntax
```javascript
new RangeError()
new RangeError(message)
```

### Constructor Parameters
- message (optional): String describing the error
- Type: string
- Default: Empty string

### Instance Properties
```javascript
RangeError.prototype.name        // "RangeError"
RangeError.prototype.constructor // RangeError function
